nodes.text: Sir Ajax Wennel was a Knight of House Cadriaan of the Tapani sector. He was a dynamic noble and a saber rake with an anti-Galactic Empire attitude. Although not a supporter of the Rebel Alliance, especially with JAN activities within the sector, Ajax saw the behavior of the Empire as a betrayal of honor. He was a guest at the Unification Gala hosted by Lady Peta Lactril prior to the Battle of Endor.
